OL,5, There was an "unjustified reliance" on 
OL,6, firefighters to evacuate Grenfell Tower
OL,7, on the night of the fatal fire, a union
OL,8, has told the inquiry into the disaster.
OL,10,FThe Fire Brigades Union said building  
OL,11,Fowners and managers should draw up     
OL,12,Fevacuation plans to prevent future     
OL,13,Fcatastrophes.                          
OL,15,FUnion lawyer Mark Seaward said there   
OL,16,Fwas a "near total failure" of fire     
OL,17,Fsafety measures at Grenfell Tower.     
OL,19,FThe June 2017 disaster at the west     
OL,20,FLondon tower block killed 72 people.   
